{"id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0003", "text": "The number of ransomware attacks worldwide has increased significantly. In October alone, 594 incidents were recorded. This amounts to an increase of 41 percent compared to September.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0003", "source_slug": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november", "source_title": "Significantly more ransomware attacks in October and November", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november.html", "source_date": "2025-12-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 3}}
{"id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0004", "text": "The industrial sector was hardest hit in October, with 167 ransomware attacks (28 percent of the total). The retail and car manufacturers sectors followed with 124 incidents. The healthcare sector recorded 64 ransomware attacks.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0004", "source_slug": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november", "source_title": "Significantly more ransomware attacks in October and November", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november.html", "source_date": "2025-12-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 4}}
{"id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0005", "text": "The ransomware group Qilin remained the most active activist group in October with 170 attacks (29 percent of the total). This was followed by Sinobi (65 attacks, 15 percent) and Akira (64 attacks, also 15 percent).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0005", "source_slug": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november", "source_title": "Significantly more ransomware attacks in October and November", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november.html", "source_date": "2025-12-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 5}}
{"id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0006", "text": "In October we enter one of the most active times of the year. Vigilance is more important than ever. Ransomware activity is increasing and large-scale attacks continue to cause economic and operational damage.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0006", "source_slug": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november", "source_title": "Significantly more ransomware attacks in October and November", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november.html", "source_date": "2025-12-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 6}}
{"id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0007", "text": "For companies in the Netherlands, these figures mean that the peak season for cyber threats has begun. There is a clear pattern of more targeted and extensive ransomware campaigns that capitalize on increased consumer activity (Black Friday, Cyber ​​Monday, holidays).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0007", "source_slug": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november", "source_title": "Significantly more ransomware attacks in October and November", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november.html", "source_date": "2025-12-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 7}}
{"id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0008", "text": "It is therefore very important that companies take immediate action. Consider:", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0008", "source_slug": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november", "source_title": "Significantly more ransomware attacks in October and November", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november.html", "source_date": "2025-12-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 8}}
{"id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0009", "text": "- Focusing and practicing incident and crisis response plans.\n- Perform proactive monitoring of systems and networks.\n- Training employees in cyber awareness, focusing on ransomware triggers.\n- Ensuring reliable, up-to-date backups and recovery procedures.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0009", "source_slug": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november", "source_title": "Significantly more ransomware attacks in October and November", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november.html", "source_date": "2025-12-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 9}}
{"id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0010", "text": "If your organization has not yet taken appropriate measures, start with an overview of your supplier and chain risks. In the context of the NIS2 directive, this is also a moment to benefit from a strategic advantage.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0010", "source_slug": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november", "source_title": "Significantly more ransomware attacks in October and November", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november.html", "source_date": "2025-12-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 10, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 10}}
{"id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0011", "text": "This article was produced in collaboration with [Samen Digitaal Veilig](https://www.samendigitaalveilig.nl/).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0011", "source_slug": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november", "source_title": "Significantly more ransomware attacks in October and November", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november.html", "source_date": "2025-12-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 11, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 11}}
{"id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0012", "text": "About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0012", "source_slug": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november", "source_title": "Significantly more ransomware attacks in October and November", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november.html", "source_date": "2025-12-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 12, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 12}}
{"id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0013", "text": "- Do you have an SME company and do you want to reduce your cyber risks? Then take a look at [Cyber ​​Fundament](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-voor-het-mkb/), especially for SME entrepreneurs.\n- Learn more about the 4-in-1 cyber solution [Cyber ​​Safe & Secure](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-veilig-en-zeker/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link) especially for large businesses and reduce your cyber risks.\n- Do you also want to [do business safely](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/veilig-ondernemen/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link)? View smart tools, useful articles and cyber webinars.\n- [Report fraud to us](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/prive/abnamro/veilig-banken/fraude-melden.html \"Report fraud\"), even if in doubt, after which our helpdesk will help you immediately.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november__a2-late-chunking__0013", "source_slug": "fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november", "source_title": "Significantly more ransomware attacks in October and November", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/cyberaanval/fors-meer-ransomware-aanvallen-in-oktober-en-november.html", "source_date": "2025-12-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "cyberaanval", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 13, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 13}}
